    "body": "Closes #8856\nCloses #8854\r\n\r\nPort NVIDIA/cuCollections#792 into the cudax HLL.\r\n\r\nReplaces the bare Hash template parameter on `hyperloglog`, `hyperloglog_ref`, and `__hyperloglog_impl` with a Policy parameter that bundles hash function, bit slicing, and finalizer into one type.\r\nAdds `default_hll_policy<Key, Hash>` reproducing the existing behavior.\r\n\r\nSuperseeds #8855.",
